1 translation units
start translation unit 1
translation-unit
  function-definition adjust function of (double) returning double
    parameter value double
    compound-statement
      expression-statement
        unary-expression lvalue double OP_INC:++
          id-expression lvalue double value
      expression-statement
        postfix-expression prvalue double OP_DEC:--
          id-expression lvalue double value
      return-statement
        id-expression lvalue double value
end translation unit
